#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are like me you have thousands of images ever since you got your "
"first camera, some taken with a normal camera other with a digital camera. "
"Through all the years you believed that until eternity you would be able to "
"remember the story behind every single picture, you would be able to "
"remember the names of all the people on your images, and you would be able "
"to remember the exact date of every single image. I personally realized that "
"this was not possible anymore, and especially for my digital images - but "
"also for my paper images - I needed a tool to help me describe my images, "
"and to search in the pile of images. This is exactly what &kphotoalbum; is "
"all about."
msgstr ""
"Če imate kot jaz na tisoče slik, odkar ste dobili svoj prvi fotoaparat, "
"nekatere posnete še z analognim fotoaparatom, druge z digitalnim "
"fotoaparatom. Skozi vsa leta ste verjeli, da se boste do večnosti lahko "
"spomnili zgodbe za vsako posamezno sliko, da se boste lahko spomnili imen "
"vseh ljudi na svojih slikah in da se boste lahko spomnili točnega datuma "
"vsake ena slika. Osebno sem ugotovil, da to ni več mogoče, in zlasti za "
"svoje digitalne slike - pa tudi za papirnate slike - sem potreboval orodje, "
"ki mi bo pomagalo opisati moje slike in za iskanje po kupu slik. To je točno "
"tisto, kar je &kphotoalbum;."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kphotoalbum; focuses on three key points:"
msgstr "&kphotoalbum; se osredotoča na tri ključne točke:"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It must be easy to annotate a number of images at a time. It must for "
"example not take more than a few mouse clicks to mark all your images from "
"your holiday as being from Italy, 1992. &kphotoalbum; offers two ways of "
"describing images: <guilabel>one at a time</guilabel>, which is useful for "
"writing text about images, and <guilabel>All Simultaneously</guilabel>, "
"which is useful for selecting a number of images, and setting properties "
"like location, people on images, and date of image."
msgstr ""
"Mora biti enostavno dodajanje opomb številnim slikam hkrati. Na primer, ne "
"sme trajati več kot nekaj klikov miške, da označite vse vaše slike z vašega "
"dopusta kot iz Italije, 1992. &kphotoalbum; ponuja dva načina opisovanja "
"slik: <guilabel>eno po eno</guilabel>, kar je uporabno za pisanje besedila o "
"slikah, in <guilabel>Vse hkrati</guilabel>, ki je uporabno za izbiro več "
"slik in nastavitev lastnosti, kot so lokacija, ljudje na slikah in datum "
"slike."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It must be easy to search for images. &kphotoalbum; offers to describe "
"images with a number of properties. These includes date, people, places, "
"plus a keyword field the user can use for custom keywords like "
"<emphasis>Album 7</emphasis> or <emphasis>Holiday trip to Italy</emphasis>. "
"With &kphotoalbum; you can search for images in each of the categories - e."
"g. find all the images with Jesper on them from the holiday in Italy. It is "
"of course possible to create your own categories, much more on that later."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje slik mora biti preprosto. &kphotoalbum; ponuja opis slik s "
"številnimi lastnostmi. To vključuje datum, ljudi, kraje in polja za ključne "
"besede, ki ga lahko uporabnik uporabi za ključne besede po meri, kot je "
"<emphasis>Album 7</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Počitniško potovanje v Italijo</"
"emphasis>. Z &kphotoalbum; slike lahko iščete v vsaki od kategorij – npr. "
"poiščite vse slike z Jesperjem s počitnic v Italiji. Seveda je možno "
"ustvariti lastne kategorije, a več o tem kasneje."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It must be easy to browse and View the images. When viewing images, your "
"focus often changes - one moment you are looking at images from your holiday "
"in 1992, and when seeing an image of a friend whom you spent that holiday "
"with, you focus suddenly changes, so you want to see all images of that "
"friend."
msgstr ""
"Brskanje in ogledovanje slik mora biti enostavno. Ko gledate slike, se vaš "
"fokus pogosto spremeni - v trenutku gledate slike s počitnic leta 1992, ko "
"vidite sliko prijatelja, s katerim ste preživeli tiste počitnice, in fokus "
"se nenadoma spremeni, zato želite videti vse slike tega  prijatelja."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of the manual"
msgstr "Pregled priročnika"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this manual I will take you through the steps of (1) annotating your "
"images, (2) browsing and viewing images and (3) advanced topics and "
"customization."
msgstr ""
"V tem priročniku vas bom popeljal skozi korake (1) označevanja vaših slik, "
"(2) brskanja in ogledovanja slik ter (3) naprednih tem in prilagajanja."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kphotoalbum; started out as an application for managing your images, but "
"since then it has been extended, so it today also takes care of your videos. "
"In many places in this manual I will talk about images, but just as often "
"the discussion does include videos."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum; se je začel kot aplikacija za upravljanje vaših slik, od "
"takrat pa se je razširila, tako da danes skrbi tudi za vaše video posnetke. "
"Na mnogih mestih v tem priročniku bom govoril o slikah, vendar prav tako "
"pogosto razprava vključuje videoposnetke."

#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organization of images and &kphotoalbum; files"
msgstr "Organizacija slik in datoteke &kphotoalbum;a"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kphotoalbum; uses all the images of a directory and all subdirectories "
"below it, first time you start &kphotoalbum;, you will be asked for the "
"location of this directory. &kphotoalbum; will not modify any images, so you "
"do not have to be afraid of &kphotoalbum; altering your images "
"<footnote><para>The two exceptions to this rule is (1) if you ask "
"&kphotoalbum; to delete individual images, from <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Selected</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, and (2) "
"plug-in operations.</para></footnote>, actually if you do not trust "
"&kphotoalbum;, feel free to make all your images write protected."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum; uporablja vse slike imenika in vseh podimenikov pod njim; ko "
"prvič zaženete &kphotoalbum;, boste vprašani za lokacijo tega imenika. "
"&kphotoalbum; ne bo spremenil nobene slike, zato se vam ni treba bati "
"&kphotoalbum;a glede spreminjanja vaših slik <footnote><para>Dve izjemi od "
"tega pravila sta (1) če vprašate &kphotoalbum; za brisanje posameznih slik, "
"iz <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši izbrano</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in (2) operacije vtičnika.</para></footnote>, "
"pravzaprav če &kphotoalbum;u ne zaupate, poskrbite, da bodo vse vaše slike "
"zaščitene pred pisanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kphotoalbum; will save all its information in the file <filename>index.xml</"
"filename> in your topmost image directory. This file is a simple XML file, "
"so you can easily back it up using whatever tools you prefer, including "
"normal backup utilities, copying the file to a floppy disk, or keeping "
"revisions using VCS. There is also a backup script (<emphasis>kpa-backup.sh</"
"emphasis>) provided in &kphotoalbum;'s sources that backs up not only the "
"index.xml but also the configuration files inside user's home directory."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum; bo vse svoje podatke shranil v datoteko <filename>index.xml</"
"filename> v vašem najvišjem imeniku slik. Ta datoteka je preprosta datoteka "
"XML, tako da jo lahko preprosto varnostno kopirate z orodji, ki jih želite, "
"vključno z običajnimi pripomočki za varnostno kopiranje, kopiranjem datoteke "
"na disketo ali ohranjanjem revizij z uporabo VCS. Obstaja tudi skript za "
"varnostno kopiranje (<emphasis>kpa-backup.sh</emphasis>), ki je na voljo v "
"virih &kphotoalbum;, ki varnostno kopira ne le index.xml, ampak tudi "
"konfiguracijske datoteke znotraj uporabnikovega domačega imenika."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kphotoalbum; will remember where you told it your images were located, and "
"reuse that in future use of &kphotoalbum;. Should you ever want to load "
"another database into &kphotoalbum; (i.e. another directory tree of images), "
"then you may start it with the <option>-c</option> option. For example: "
"<userinput><command>kphotoalbum</command> <option>-c</option> <filename>~/"
"CompanyImages/index.xml</filename></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum; si bo zapomnil, kje ste mu povedali, da se vaše slike "
"nahajajo, in to ponovno uporabil pri prihodnji uporabi &kphotoalbum;a. Če bi "
"kdaj želeli naložiti drugo zbirko podatkov v &kphotoalbum; (tj. drugo "
"imeniško drevo slik), potem ga lahko zaženete z možnostjo <option>-c</"
"option>. Na primer: <userinput><command>kphotoalbum</command> <option>-c</"
"option> <filename>~/CompanyImages/index.xml</filename></userinput>."
